			<H2 CLASS='western'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><FONT SIZE=2>Article
			1 – License</FONT></FONT></H2>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				Rightsholders herewith grant the Retransmission Operator the
				non-exclusive license to retransmit to its subscribers the
				programmes and the works contained therein in so far as the
				Rightsholders hold rights to these works, transmitted by the
				Broadcasters indicated in Enclosure 1 and Enclosure 2 which form
				an integral part of this Agreement.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.25in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=2>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				Rightsholders listed in Enclosure 1 and Enclosure 2 guarantee:</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL TYPE=a>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>their
				neighbouring rights as Broadcasters and as producers in so far as
				the Broadcasters own or acquired copyrights and neighbouring
				rights or hold derived copyrights and neighbouring rights ,
				either by law or by contract </FONT>
				</P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.52in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL TYPE=a START=2>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>author’s
				rights and neighbouring rights other than the ones mentioned
				before, as far as these rights are acquired by the broadcaster,
				either by law or by contract</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.52in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.52in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL TYPE=a START=3>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>Broadcasters
				are not responsible for any third party claims concerning rights
				that are not acquired by them, such as – but not limited to -
				composers’ rights or audiovisual authors’ rights which are
				managed by other collecting societies or other rights holders.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>All
			other rights have to be acquired by the Retransmission Operator
			from the competent collecting and/or copyright societies.</FONT></P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=3>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				Retransmission Operator accepts the authorization referred to in
				paragraph 1 of this article.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=4>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				Rightsholders herewith state and the Retransmission Operator
				acknowledges that the license mentioned in paragraph 1 of this
				article covers the period from 1st January 2015 to 31st December
				2017.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<H2 CLASS='western'><BR>
			</H2>
			<H2 CLASS='western'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><FONT SIZE=2>Article
			2 – Scope of License</FONT></FONT></H2>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><U>General
				Conditions:</U></FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>Without
					prejudice to Article 7 of this Agreement, the retransmission of
					the programmes of the Broadcasters referred to in this Agreement
					must be simultaneous, unchanged and unabridged, and without
					additions or substitutions.</FONT></P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.42in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			 
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a START=2>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
					permission granted under the terms of this Agreement
					specifically does not cover retransmission in segmented packages
					for which the subscriber has to pay a separate fee for each
					channel (no à la carte service). It is understood that the
					retransmission will occur only in the basic package. </FONT>
					</P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.42in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.42in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.42in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a START=3>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>In
					case the retransmission occurs in an extended package, the
					permission is granted only under the condition that</FONT></P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a>
					<OL TYPE=i>
						<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>at
						least 10 channels are in the same package showing the cultural
						variety and</FONT></P>
						<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>the
						package is the second most distributed and</FONT></P>
						<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>no
						content related fee is charged by the retransmission operator
						to the subscriber for a specific channel.</FONT></P>
					</OL>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a START=4>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>In
					order to make the identity of the various programmes apparent,
					the Retransmission Operator will in principle dedicate a
					specific channel to the retransmission of the programmes of each
					particular television network station. He will inform its
					subscribers of its decisions in this matter. </FONT>
					</P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=2>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><U>Special
				Conditions for IPTV (xDSL) Retransmission:</U></FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>In
			case of IPTV retransmission the license is limited to the
			ADSL/IPTV retransmission of these TV channels. ADSL/IPTV means
			Internet Protocol television, a form of cable distribution,
			whereby audiovisual content is distributed to subscribers using a
			broadband connection with a dedicated bandwidth allocation so that
			the vision and audio is such that the end user receives sound and
			pictures that&nbsp;meet or exceed the required minimum technical
			quality standards of 5Mbs which are delivered to a reception
			device identifiable by a unique IP number within a closed
			network.&nbsp;The IPTV retransmission is subject to the following
			conditions:</FONT></P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 1in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
					time delay caused by encryption must not be longer than 10
					seconds.</FONT></P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a START=2>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
					retransmission of the program is only permitted within a
					closed-circuit group of users. Only the households registered by
					the Retransmission Operator may have access to the programs. The
					Retransmission Operator has to ensure the control over the
					program signals all the way from his home base to the users.</FONT></P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a START=3>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
					Retransmission Operator has to ensure that there is no
					connection to the World Wide Web. The Retransmission Operator
					has to ensure technically and legally, that the programs cannot
					be transmitted to the World Wide Web.</FONT></P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a START=4>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
					Retransmission Operator will allow reception only by set
					top-boxes combined with TV-Sets.</FONT></P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a START=5>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
					Retransmission Operator has to ensure that neither he or the
					user nor any third persons may alter or shorten the programs nor
					add parts to it. The Retransmission Operator has to ensure that
					the programs are visible on the full TV-screen (no split
					screens, public screening etc.). The Retransmission Operator is
					not permitted to add program signals or commercials to the
					program signals. This refers to parts of the programs as well as
					to the commercials partly or totally.</FONT></P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a START=6>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>Time-shift
					retransmission is not allowed.</FONT></P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=3>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><FONT SIZE=2><U><SPAN STYLE='font-weight: normal'>Special
				Conditions for DTH, Mobile and Web Applications</SPAN></U></FONT></FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.25in; margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>This
			license provided through this Agreement does not cover permission
			for usage of the channels in DTH, Mobile and Web Applications as
			the Rightsholders currently do not hold respective rights for all
			of the channels they represent. Licenses for DTH and mobile usages
			of some of the channels represented by VGM (Enclosure 2) may be
			acquired through separate Agreements. The Rightsholders agree to
			discuss licenses for any further services in good faith once the
			Rightsholders hold the respective rights in the future.</FONT></P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<H2 CLASS='western'><BR>
			</H2>
			<H2 CLASS='western'><BR>
			</H2>
			<H2 CLASS='western'><BR>
			</H2>
			<H2 CLASS='western'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><FONT SIZE=2>Article
			3 – No Recordings or Interruptions</FONT></FONT></H2>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
			Retransmission Operator is not allowed to carry out recordings of
			the programmes covered by this Agreement or the works contained in
			those programmes, neither is he permitted to interrupt or alter
			the programmes by any means or by any form other than for
			technical reasons or due to legal obligations.</FONT></P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<H3 CLASS='western'><BR>
			</H3>
			<H3 CLASS='western'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><FONT SIZE=2>Article
			4 – Exceptional Revocation</FONT></FONT></H3>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				Rightsholders reserve the right to prohibit in exceptional cases
				the retransmission of programmes or specific programme parts
				thereof. This right shall only be exercised in cases of objective
				and absolute necessity in order to avoid serious and lasting
				infringement of the interests of the Rightsholders or to protect
				the rights of third parties concerned by the content of the
				programme.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.22in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.22in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.22in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=2>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>Every
				such revocation of the authorization must be communicated,
				together with a statement of its reasons, to the Retransmission
				Operator at least 96 hours in advance of the scheduled
				retransmission.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<H2 CLASS='western'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><FONT SIZE=2>Article
			5 – Third Party Rights</FONT></FONT></H2>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>If
				the Rightsholders become aware prior to the retransmission that
				the retransmission of programme parts of the TV channels covered
				by the present Agreement might cause legal and technical problems
				with regard to the retransmission in BULGARIA, they shall
				immediately inform the Retransmission Operator about the imminent
				problem and try to settle the rights issue. If the Rightsholders
				cannot settle the rights issue they will ask the Retransmission
				Operators to black out the programme part according to Article 4
				of the present Agreement. </FONT>
				</P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=2>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				extent of the indemnification referred to in the preceding
				paragraph shall be restricted to the sum which would have been
				payable to the party submitting the claim for the use of the
				relevant programme or a work of the same nature as the disputed
				work or programme, if that party were represented by the
				competent rightowner involved in the present Agreement. The
				indemnification is furthermore restricted to claims submitted up
				to three years after the date on which the work or programme was
				retransmitted via the cable system.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=3>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				Rightsholders shall indemnify the Retransmission Operator under
				the further condition that the Retransmission Operator inform
				immediately the Rightsholders (through Virgin Limited) about the
				third party’s claim and provide them with all the information
				and documentation concerning the claim submitted.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<H2 CLASS='western'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><FONT SIZE=2>Article
			6 - Termination</FONT></FONT></H2>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>Rightsholders
				have the right to terminate the Agreement with prompt effect if
				Retransmission Operator has failed to settle his obligation under
				this Agreement, especially if: </FONT>
				</P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>the
					retransmission operator has failed to settle his obligation
					resulting from Article 2 and 3 of this Agreement, or</FONT></P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.52in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.52in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<OL TYPE=a START=2>
					<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>if
					the Retransmission Operator has not paid the remuneration
					stipulated in this Agreement for the term longer than three
					months.</FONT></P>
				</OL>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=2>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>Before
				terminating the Agreement, the Rightsholders will remind the
				Retransmission Operator in writing, that he did not respect the
				proper term and will allow 30 day period in which the
				Retransmission Operator must fulfill his obligations, otherwise
				the Agreement will be terminated. If it is obvious that the
				Retransmission Operator is avoiding the receipt of the written
				reminder, so that it returns to the Rightsholders two times, the
				Agreement will be terminated without any written note. </FONT>
				</P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=3>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				right to claim damages, however, is not affected by the provision
				referred to in the preceding paragraph.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=4>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>In
				addition, broadcasting organizations may stop their broadcasting
				service with prompt effect in such exceptional case if and when
				it is demanded for the respective broadcasting organization by
				compelling legal or economic reasons. In this case the license
				granted by the Rightsholders through this Agreement ends with the
				day the broadcast is stopped.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<H2 CLASS='western' STYLE='margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in'><BR>
			</H2>
			<H2 CLASS='western' STYLE='margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><FONT SIZE=2>Article
			7 – Programmes Abide by Legislation of Country of Their Origin</FONT></FONT></H2>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
			Rightsholders are in no respect responsible neither liable with
			regard to legal actions by natural or legal persons who might
			perceive a threat to their honour or in any other way or who have
			suffered harm as a result of the above mentioned retransmission,
			subject that those programmes correspond to the legislation of the
			country of their origin.</FONT></P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<H3 CLASS='western'><BR>
			</H3>
			<H3 CLASS='western'><BR>
			</H3>
			<H3 CLASS='western'><BR>
			</H3>
			<H3 CLASS='western'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><FONT SIZE=2>Article
			8 – Remuneration </FONT></FONT>
			</H3>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				authorization for the cable retransmission of the programmes and
				the works protected by copyright, subject to this Agreement, is
				given in return to the payment of the remuneration agreed in this
				article, beginning from the 1st January 2015, calculated on a 3
				month basis.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=2>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				payable remuneration is depending on the number of the
				retransmitted programmes and the number of subscribers.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=3>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				remuneration per month per subscriber per channel in SD is 0,050
				BGN (0,027 EUR). </FONT>
				</P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=4>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>After
				2015, the abovementioned tariffs will increase yearly by 7 %.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=5>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>VAT
				is to be added to the sum fee calculated as written in previous
				paragraphs of this article. Any taxes, fees etc. – if
				applicable - including, but not limited to VAT have to be covered
				by the Retransmission Operator.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=6>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>Virgin
				Ltd. is entitled to collect the agreed remuneration quarterly
				from the Retransmission Operator, in the name and on behalf of
				the Rightsholders. Trimesters are to be counted beginning from
				1st of January. The Retransmission Operator has to pay the
				remuneration within 30 (thirty) days after the receipt of an
				invoice for the previous trimester, issued by Virgin Ltd. in the
				name and on behalf of the Rightsholders. The amount contained in
				the invoice will be calculated in EUR.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=7>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				parties will start negotiations for the tariff applicable from
				1</FONT><SUP><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>st</FONT></SUP><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>
				of January 2018 onwards by 1</FONT><SUP><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>st</FONT></SUP><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>
				of June 2017.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<FONT FACE='Arial, serif'><FONT SIZE=2><U><SPAN STYLE='font-weight: normal'>Article
			9 - Reporting</SPAN></U></FONT></FONT></P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.49in; text-indent: -0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				Retransmission Operator is obliged to provide Virgin Ltd. with
				all relevant data for the execution of this Agreement that is
				necessary for the calculation of the remuneration payable to the
				Rightsholders. Communication of the data mentioned above to
				Virgin Ltd. be carried out in every quarter of a year with
				respect to the data valid on the last day of the last month of
				the respective quarter of the year until at the latest the 15th
				day of this month. Following this communication of the data
				mentioned above to Virgin Ltd. the Retransmission Operator may
				not modify the package of channels retransmitted by them within
				the respective quarter of the year.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=2>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>If
				the Retransmission Operator has not paid the amount on the date
				mentioned above, he will as of this day in addition be liable to
				the payment of legal interest.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=3>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>Virgin
				Ltd. is entitled to audit the number of subscribers of the
				Retransmission Operator. If the Rightsholders require an
				additional audit this would be possible, but the costs will be
				charged to the Rightsholders, unless, the result of this audit
				differs more than 10% with respect to the payments due to the
				Rightsholders.</FONT></P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=4>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>The
				Retransmission Operator shall report in writing within fifteen
				(15) days after the signing of this Agreement to Virgin Ltd. the
				composition of the television programme package which is being
				offered by him to its subscribers. Changes made in the package
				after that date could only be made according to the 1</FONT><SUP><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>st</FONT></SUP><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>
				paragraph of this article. </FONT>
				</P>
			</OL>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-left: 0.22in; text-indent: -0.2in; margin-bottom: 0in'>
			<BR>
			</P>
			<OL START=5>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>Without
				prejudice to the terms of this Agreement, interruptions of
				programmes, as referred to in Article 4 of this Agreement shall
