				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>Technical
				interruptions of emissions for reasons which fall within the
				competence of the Broadcasting Corporations involved shall not
				have an effect on the total amount payable under the terms of
				this Agreement, except in the case and insofar as they result in
				an effective reduction of the amount payable by the subscribers
				to the Retransmission Operator.</FONT></P>
