			<OL START=7>
				<LI><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-bottom: 0in'><FONT FACE='Arial, serif'>In
				the case of application of withholding taxes, the broadcasters
				will provide the cable operator with confirmation of residence by
				their national tax authority to get an exemption from tax
				liability in BULGARIA. The cable operator shall promptly provide
				the broadcasters with all applicable withholding tax forms issued
				by the tax authorities of BULGARIA and provide reasonable
				assistance to the broadcasters in maintaining their exemption
				from withholding tax liability in BULGARIA in relation to the
				payments due under this Agreement. Also, the cable operator shall
				provide the broadcasters with all the documents evidencing a tax
				withholding (i.e. a Statement issued by the local tax
				authorities) to allow the broadcasters to recover such
				withholding taxes in their own country. The abovementioned
				documents/declarations shall be forwarded to the broadcaster
				before 31st March of each year; if the cable operator falls to do
				so within the abovementioned terms, the broadcasters will be
				forced to recover amounts from such withholding and request
				payment of the amount deducted by issuing a separate invoice for
				the sum not remitted to their bank account.</FONT></P>
