			<H2 LANG='en-GB' CLASS='western' STYLE='margin-left: 0.02in'><FONT SIZE=2>4.3.
			Advance Payment – If the Operator has less than 2000
			Subscribers, Operator agrees to pay ECTV the Subscriber Fee six
			months in advance during the Term. The advance payment shall be
			based on the number of subscribers as of the Commencement Date for
			the first six month period and then for each following six month
			period based on the Reports provided in accordance with clause 5
			for the previous six month period.  At the end of each relevant
			six month period of the Term, ECTV will invoice or credit the
			Operator for any difference between the Advance Payment and the
			actual amount due for that six month period based on the Reports. 
			</FONT>
