			of remedy entitling ECTV to terminate.</FONT></H2>
			<H2 LANG='en-GB' CLASS='western' STYLE='margin-left: 0.02in'><FONT SIZE=2>4.5.
			Exclusive of VAT - The amounts payable by the Operator to ECTV
			shall be exclusive of VAT which shall be payable by the Operator. </FONT>
