			<H2 LANG='en-GB' CLASS='western' STYLE='margin-left: 0.02in'><FONT SIZE=2>4.12.Throughout
			the Term, for one year after the expiry of the Term (&quot;</FONT><FONT SIZE=2><B>Audit
