<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>For
the avoidance of doubt, Subscribers shall mean all and any cable
subscribers listed as recipients of the Channels in Operator’s
service at the beginning of each month when a fee is due under this
contract, and “Average Number of Subscribers” shall mean the
arithmetical average between the number of Subscribers at the
beginning of a given month and the number of Subscribers at the end
of such month.  A precise monthly statement indicating the number of
viewers and Subscribers will be sent to Licensor by Operator.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
 <FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>4.3.
Unless otherwise agreed in writing by the Licensor, all prices shall
be stated and payments made in Euros (€).  Payment shall be due at
the beginning of each month of service of activity upon receipt of
invoice. The invoice will be issued quarterly payable at receipt of
the invoice.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%; page-break-after: avoid'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><B>5.</B></FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>
</FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><U><B>OBLIGATIONS
OF OPERATOR</B></U></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>5.1.
Use the satellite signal feeds in real time streams through its
network, notwithstanding the necessary delay due to the normal
technical intervention to make the streams suitable for cable
distribution.  In particular, any form of local storage for delayed
distribution (e.g. PPV) is excluded.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>5.2.
Diligently promote the Channels, and use its best efforts to expand
the expansion of Channels in its cable service within the Territory.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>5.3.
Be solely responsible for its selection of customers and business
model to its customers and be solely responsible for payment of
Channels in accordance with the Licensor’s credit terms then in
effect, regardless of whether or not the customer pays the Operator,
unless otherwise agreed to in advance in writing by Licensor.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>5.4.
Promptly inform Licensor of the activities of potential competitors
in the Territory and of any laws and/or regulations in the Territory
which may affect the sale of the Channels or which may be related to
safety, labeling or other requirements with respect to the Channels.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>5.5.
Diligently abide by any applicable laws and regulation in the
Territory regarding TV signals in general and adult content in
particular.  In effect, it is the policy of Licensor to demand that
content is scrambled (encrypted) at all times and therefore not
accessible without the proper authorization, in an effort to protect
minors from viewing the content. Operator agrees to deploy
conditional access technology that is at least the more secure of (i)
set-top boxes, or (ii) such more secure conditional access technology
as Licensor applies as a minimum standard (for example, a decoder
based system). Operator agrees to strictly enforce such policy on its
network and shall ensure that no part of the Channels is received
unencrypted or at any location where an admission fee, cover charge,
minimum or like sum is charged, which is public or common area.
Licensor may suspend or terminate this Agreement if Operator fails to
maintain appropriate signal security levels.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>5.6.
Not use any advertising, promotional or selling materials in relation
to the Channels except with Licensor’s prior written approval (such
approval not to be unreasonably withheld); provided, however, that if
Licensor has not responded to Operator’s request for approval
within five (5) business days of Licensor’s receipt of such
request, such approval will be deemed given.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>5.7.
Not make any promise or representation or give any warranty or other
benefit in favor of any customer or to the detriment of Licensor, or
assume any liability or obligation on behalf of Licensor, whether in
relation to the Channels or otherwise, without Licensor’s express
prior written consent.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>5.8.
Indemnify, defend and hold harmless Licensor from any claims,
demands, liabilities, actions, suits or proceedings including
expenses and attorneys’ fees, asserted, claimed or made by
Operator, its agents, servants, employees, customers or users, which
arise from Operator’s negligence or Operator’s breach of its
obligations hereunder.  This shall survive termination or
non-renewal.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%; page-break-inside: avoid'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><B>6.
INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY</B></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>6.1.
Operator</FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>
acknowledges the exclusive right, title and interest of Licensor in
any present or future trade mark or trade name associated with the
Channels of the Licensor</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>6.2.
The Licensor </FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>authorizes</FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>
the Operator to use the Trade Marks in the Territory on or in
relation to the Channels on a basis consistent with this Agreement
and for the purposes only of exercising the Operators rights </FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>in
performing its obligations under this agreement.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>6.3.
During the term of this agreement, Operator as a user of the object
of protection shall make all necessary payments, declarations and
other obligations under applicable law and/or agreements (concluded
with collective organizations pursuant to applicable law) to the
collective management of copyrights organizations that have the
authority, pursuant to applicable law, to collect royalties on the
distribution of radio and television programming. Operator shall
ensure that the agreements with such organizations include all
artistic performance and works and shall have sole responsibility for
clearance and payment of such obligation without any right to reclaim
it from Licensor.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><B>7.
</B></FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><U><B>WARRANTIES</B></U></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>7.1.
Licensor warrants it is a fully licensed broadcasting company from
Italy and that it holds the necessary rights for cable distribution
of its streams in the Territory.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><B>8.</B></FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>
</FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><U><B>TRADE
SECRETS</B></U></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>8.1.
Each party shall take all reasonable care to protect any trade
secrets and confidential information which may be acquired from the
other party whether or not in writing or otherwise through the course
of dealings (hereinafter referred to as “Confidential
Information”).</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>8.2.
Operator agrees that disclosure by Licensor of any of the
Confidential Information, whether written, oral, machine-readable
form or otherwise, is made in strictest confidence. Also, Licensor
agrees that disclosure by Operator of any of the Confidential
Information, whether written, oral, machine-readable form or
otherwise, is made in strictest confidence.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%; page-break-after: avoid'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><B>9.</B></FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>
</FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><U><B>SUSPENSION
AND TERMINATION</B></U></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%; page-break-after: avoid'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><U>9.1.
Licensor shall be entitled to suspend the provision of the Channels
to Operator at any moment in case of: </U></FONT></FONT>
</P>
<UL>
	<LI><P CLASS='western' STYLE='text-indent: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
	<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><U>a
	breach of the signal security or regulatory provisions referred to
	in Article 5.5. herein above and/or</U></FONT></FONT></P>
	<LI><P CLASS='western' STYLE='text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'><U>
	<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>a
	delay in payment of the monthly fees due by Operator of more than 30
	days. </U></FONT></FONT>
	</P>
</UL>
<P CLASS='western' STYLE='text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><U>After
such breach is cured, Operator shall have the right to request the
restoring of the signal.</U></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%; page-break-after: avoid'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>9.2.
This Agreement may be terminated with cause upon notice by certified
or return receipt requested mail, which shall become effective ninety
(90) days after receipt, which shall be deemed to have occurred (5)
days after mailing.  To the extent that the form of notice or the
time period of notice permitted herein shall conflict with applicable
law, then such alternate form of notice or notice period of such
applicable law shall be deemed to be incorporated into this
Agreement.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%; page-break-inside: avoid'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>9.3.
To the extent that the Licensor shall elect to terminate this
Agreement for good cause, good cause shall be any of the following:</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>9.3.1.
Failure by the Operator to make timely payment of any obligation
owing to the Licensor, exceeding 15 days from the payment due date. </FONT></FONT>
</P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>9.3.2.
A misrepresentation to the Licensor by the Operator or by any
principal owner or principal manager in applying for the appointment
as the Operator under this Agreement or, after appointment, as to the
records of the Operator, the status of current accounts or orders for
Channels or concerning the beneficial ownership or management of the
Operator;</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>9.3.3.
Willful failure of the Operator to comply with the provisions of any
law or regulation relating to the operation of its business as a
Operator or to the sales or servicing of the Channels;</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>9.3.4.
Failure by the Operator to perform any of the other obligations or
responsibilities under this Agreement which continues for a period of
ninety days after notice thereof from the Licensor.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>9.4.
In the event either party shall be declared a bankrupt or insolvent,
or have a receiver appointed over its property or shall petition for
reorganization or other remedy under the bankruptcy laws as now or
hereafter existing, or make any assignment for the benefit of
creditors or pursue any other remedy under any other insolvency laws,
to the extent permitted by law, this Agreement may be terminated by
either party, effective immediately upon the mailing of a notice of
such termination by certified or return receipt requested mail.  </FONT></FONT>
</P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>In
the event of termination of this Agreement under this chapter, all
amounts owed to the Licensor shall be immediately due and payable in
accordance with the normal terms and conditions of sale in this
Agreement.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%; page-break-inside: avoid'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><B>10.</B></FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>
</FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><U><B>ASSIGNMENT</B></U></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>Operator
shall not assign or otherwise transfer all or any its rights and
obligations hereunder except with Licensor’s prior written approval
such approval should be done or denied in 15 days from the moment the
Operator notify the Licensor. </FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>
Licensor reserves the right, however, to assign and/or transfer all
or any of its rights and obligations hereunder without the prior
consent of Operator to Licensor’s parent company or to any
subsidiary or affiliated company of Licensor’s or to any third
party in connection with the sale or transfer of all or a substantial
portion of the business of the Licensor.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><B>11.</B></FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>
</FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><U><B>MISCELLANEOUS</B></U></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>11.1.
This Agreement will be construed and enforceable in accordance with
the laws of </FONT></FONT><FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'><B>Italy.</B></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>11.2.
Agreement contains the entire agreement of the parties and may only
be modified in writing, signed by the authorized representative of
the party against whom it is sought to be enforced.</FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS='western' ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE='margin-right: 0.41in; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 150%; page-break-inside: avoid; page-break-after: avoid'>
<FONT FACE='Times New Roman, serif'><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE='font-size: 11pt'>IN
WITNESS WHEREOF, the parties hereto have executed this Agreement the
day and year first above written.</FONT></FONT></P>
